<div class="col small col-sm-3 text-sm-right">
<a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.vdb-loi.com/indo_publications/navigating-a-complex-web/" target="_blank"><div style="display:inline-block;color:#3C5A99;"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square fa-2x"></i></div></a>
